------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains the files to run webservice based in 
flask microframework modeled with layers.
Each layer has a functions to manipuling the data to construct
a json data type aspect.

To connect and access the database, sqlite_layer, operate the 
information level of SQL and sends this data to dic_layer,
which converts to the dictionary type and sends it to the 
web service application layer using a framework tool for 
construct the return JSON from a data dictionary.

